title: Out - Outdoor-Floor and Table lamps
description: A romantic response to the global transition to life outside, the Out floor lamp brings the intimacy of indoor lighting outdoors. Suitable for illuminating a table or meeting point, and evocative of a flower bending with the weight of its petals in summer, this luminaire emanates with a soft, diffuse downlight, its source obscured by a translucent diffuser. Coated in a matte finish that grants a certain tenderness, the Out outdoor lampâ€™s design is enhanced by six earthy and natural tones.
